rating_comment: Lovely stay at a great place. Would recommend to all
She is nice lady managing the guest house. We reach Siliguri very late at midnight. But she managed a smooth checkin. The stuffs have been very helpful and courtecious.

Overall it was a good stay, though for a night. Rooms were clean, host were friendly and communication was thorough. It has got a spacious parking place. Even a cafe is just inside the compound. Will surely recommend to fellow travellers.
Location is good, rooms are specious and clean.
Hassle free Service, great Host, Awesome response, great cleanliness
Such a great place for short or long stays. Safe, stylish and well located.

I booked the apartment for my parents and they were all Praises for the apartment. From the time of Check-in to checkout my parents had a smooth and hassle free stay.
It is put up on a location quite away from the hustle and bustle of the city. It has ample of parking space and the apartment has all the basic amenities. I would recommend it to people.
